Rio is a respected broadcaster,

51
00:02:08,259 --> 00:02:09,360
documentary filmmaker,

52
00:02:09,819 --> 00:02:11,520
start-up investor in We Are 8,

53
00:02:11,639 --> 00:02:13,419
a social media platform for good,

54
00:02:13,860 --> 00:02:15,759
a father of five and respected

55
00:02:15,759 --> 00:02:18,180
for his leadership qualities from a young age.

56
00:02:18,219 --> 00:02:19,620
Rio, it's great to catch up with you.

57
00:02:19,639 --> 00:02:20,419
Thanks for taking the time.

58
00:02:20,520 --> 00:02:22,520
It's an extraordinary life that you've led

59
00:02:22,520 --> 00:02:24,680
and look back at your professional career,

60
00:02:24,819 --> 00:02:25,819
captaining Manchester United,

61
00:02:25,960 --> 00:02:26,599
captaining England.

62
00:02:27,060 --> 00:02:28,259
When I read that back to you,

63
00:02:28,419 --> 00:02:30,699
what are the thoughts on when you reflect back on your career?

64
